Fasasi Mobolaji Gaius, onye a maara dị ka Da Emperor, bụ nwa amaala Naịjirịa na-eti egwu, onye na-eme ihe nkiri, na onye na-ede egwu. O nwere mgbọrọgwụ ezinụlọ na Ogun Steeti, Naịjirịa. Ọ na-eti egwu n'asụsụ ala ya, Yoruba, ma na-etinye Pidgin na Bekee. Da Emperor edekọwo egwu ya na ndị egwu dịka Gabriel Afolayan, Small Doctor, na Oritse Femi.
O wepụtara egwu ya nke abụọ akpọrọ "Firewood", nke nwere olu sitere n'aka Oritse Femi
Nke a sochiri egwu "Shake it" na "I'm a Sinner".
E nyere Da Emperor ọkwa nke onye nnọchi anya njem nlegharị anya na Septemba 3rd, 2021 site na Bauchi State Tourism Board.
N'afọ 2013, ya na onye na-ese reggae nke Jamaica bụ Kisco rụkọrọ ọrụ
Da Emperor edekọwo egwu ya na ndị na-ese ihe na ndị na-abịa n'ihu

Ya na Davido na Tiwa Savage esorola ihe nkiri ahụ. N'ọnwa Febụwarị afọ 2013, e gosipụtara ya na egwu "Be Ma Boo" nke onye egwu Afro-Pop bụ Slim Joe. N'afọ 2013, o wepụtara otu egwu "Para Mode" nke Indomix gwakọtara; vidiyo egwu ya agafeela 100,000 YouTube ma wepụta ya n'afọ 2014.
Na 2 Febụwarị 2014, o wepụtara egwu iji kwado mkpọsa Gọvanọ Akinwunmi Ambode. Otu "Liar" nọchiri ya, mkpuchi nke "Loyal" nke Chris Brown gosipụtara Lil Wayne na Tyga.
N'ọnwa Mee afọ 2015, ya na Oritse Femi jikọrọ aka wepụta egwu "Firewood" nke indomix gwakọtara

N'abalị iri na abụọ n'ọnwa Febụwarị afọ 2016, o wepụtara egwu a nabatara nke ọma "I'm a Sinner". Na 5 Machị 2016, Da Emperor tinyere aka na mmekorita mba ụwa ya na onye na-ese ihe na America bụ Stylezz na onye na-ese ihe n'asụsụ Bekee bụ Shyboss
Naanị ụbọchị ole na ole mgbe ọ wụchara egwu Olamide "who u epp", nsụgharị Da Emperor kụrụ nọmba 4 na Spotify, nke onye egwu Naịjirịa bụ Olamide wepụtara egwu.
